NOTICE: Hook is 100% untested! I wrote this as a request but my development WHMCS is in use so I have no way to test this right now. Once I free up my development install I'll be able to test this.

Add Credit On Immediate Cancellation Hook for WHMCS by KuJoe (JMD.cc)
	
//Requirements:
None.

//Installation:
1) Edit the $adminuser line in canclledcredit.php ($minpay and $desc are optional).
2) Upload cancelledcredit.php into your WHMCS's hooks directory (/includes/hooks/).

//Additional Information:
None.